title: ASUS Mechanical Gaming Keyboard ROG Claymore Cherry MX Brown
feature: ASUS Aura ROG Sync for a customizable light-show with the growing ASUS Aura ecosystem including mouse, motherboard and graphics card via ROG Armoury’s 14 lighting effects
Cherry MX RGB switches for faster response times and extended keyboard life cycle
Detachable numeric keypad attaches to left for macros or right for 10-key usage
One-click overclocking, profile-switching, boot-up and fan control through programmed hot keys
Aluminum-alloy frame for enhanced durability and keypad stability
description: A powerful combination of work hard, play harder, the ROG Claymore combines responsive Cherry MX Brown switches with ASUS Aura Sync that enables unified lighting across all Aura Sync-capable devices. Choose from three different placements with the detachable numeric keypad, featuring a metal cover and spring connection for seamless movement.
